straylight-compositor (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * straylight-compositor: wlroots-based Wayland compositor
  * Tiling layout engine with workspace management
  * Layer-shell protocol support for panels and docks
  * Session lock with PAM authentication
  * D-Bus IPC via org.straylight.Compositor1

